George McKay (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_McKay_(actor) 0 George McKay (15 April 1884 - 3 December 1945) was a Russian-American actor. He appeared in more than one hundred films from 1929 to 1946. George_McKay ( 15_April_1884 - 3_December_1945 ) was a_Russian-American_actor .
